"k.i.-" en comments "By weaving relationships between individuals and groups, the gift unifies society. A prototype of reciprocity and exchange, it provides one of the main material supports of the social relationship. The gift is diversified into money and merchandise, into gifts and festivals."
"k.i.-" en translations "gift"
"k.i.-" en translations "technique of exchange"
"k.i.-" fr comments "En tissant les rapports entre les personnes et les groupes, le don unifie la société. Prototype de la réciprocité et de l'échange, il fournit l'un des principaux supports matériels de la relation sociale. Le don se diversifie en monnaie et marchandise, en cadeau et en fête."
